{"type": "article", "id": 33104, "title": "阿里巴巴再次被列入售假黑名单，以及，Diesel日本30年系列不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-10T02:48:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13127, "name": "AAFA"}, {"id": 33743, "name": "黄金周"}, {"id": 33744, "name": "赴港旅游"}, {"id": 33745, "name": "圣诞限定彩妆"}, {"id": 1160, "name": "淘宝"}, {"id": 1258, "name": "YSL"}, {"id": 2147, "name": "Blue Bottle"}, {"id": 2488, "name": "J.Crew"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 33746, "name": "Deisel"}, {"id": 33747, "name": "Samsonite"}, {"id": 2115, "name": "Hedi Slimane"}, {"id": 23194, "name": "KAWS"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161010102146yqXxV7zwI1B3jguv.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://apparel.edgl.com/news/AAFA-Puts-Pressure-on-Alibaba-Counterfeits107312\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>AAFA 要求再次将阿里巴巴列入恶名市场名单</b></a> | 代表超过 1000 个美国品牌的 American Apparel &amp; Footwear Association ( AAFA ) 再发呼吁，要求 USTR （美国贸易代表办公室）再次将阿里巴巴列入 Notorious Market 恶名市场的名单。AAFA 在给 USTR 的建议信中称，阿里巴巴未能履行 USTR 杜绝平台售假的建议。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.chinesetoday.com/big/article/1141354\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>黄金周赴港内地游客增加 7%，但零售业并无受益</b></a> | 据香港入境处数字显示，今年黄金周赴港内地游客增加了约 7%，其中，团体游客减少，个人游客则有近两位数的增长。不过，内地游客的扫货现象已经不多，今年国庆假期期间，相关零售行业的营业额同比下降 5% 至 20%。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.wmagazine.com/story/hedi-slimane-legal-drama-with-saint-laurent-and-kering-isnt-over\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>YSL 前任创意总监 Hedi Slimane 胜诉 YSL，获 1300 万美元赔偿</b></a> | 今年六月，Hedi Slimane 就 YSL 母公司开云集团单方面取消“竞业禁止义务”条款提起诉讼，最终 Hedi Slimane 胜诉。据 <a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/hedi-slimane-twitter-tirade-saint-laurent-lawsiot-10657369/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd 报道</a>，Hedi Slimane 再次起诉开云集团，要求追加赔偿金额 220 万美元，补偿他去年在职期间应得的可变薪酬部分。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>为了庆祝时尚网站 Style.com 重新运作，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/vetements-style-com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 再度推出了它的 2014 春夏系列</a>。该系列少了搞怪的元素，回归简约风格，重新演绎了品牌在两年前大热的牛仔裤、皮夹克、卫衣等多款单品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101002284Z1kbwAhEM8iDBK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101010022979zLZ4lVM6aC3ofD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100229Px0aDw8nlcTjdobe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101002291IwVfqRHr5sW2PbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100229K1Mnvp9XY4ySORkd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100229Qgh9ZGjC7SbpmJWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100237UScPjG9WmFY3sZXb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100238xD1HKGoyFjCPV2Z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101002462rfxGStdAXlIKuVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101002474yLMzuYbvVUxXgCo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">啊，终于可以随时喝到 Blue Bottle 出品的咖啡了。日前，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/blue-bottle-perfectly-ground-coffee\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blue Bottle Coffee 推出全新的包装研磨咖啡粉</a>，共有 Three Africans、Giant Steps、Bella Donovan 及 Decaf Noir 四个风味，每盒研磨咖啡粉共有 5 包，已经以每盒 17.50 美元的价格在美国率先发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100308FGQxLqfwAkNBWCrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667124\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/a-bathing-ape-x-samsonite-red-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 与箱包专家 Samsonite 旗下的 RED 支线合作</a>，发布了联名包款。这个系列共有三个部分，包括<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/a-bathing-ape-x-samsonite-red-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> </a>Bias Jack 两款不同尺寸的背包，Swing Mode 手提包，以及大容量的 The Item 旅行袋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100333VFeLYC2iro4w7XMG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100341ECH8L76lmSQcfkY9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101003430Jf9PukxrwqQdXNO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101003442K48qVkNdI0OJERw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100344whLA7x1YCKNMGlaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100344QK3GgMcTbNoIxajU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100344DL5SuENhKdj7n1sq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100344CeI8jWSorXMUGnO0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101010034683Ds4kWcYTFC9jOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100346Rl4BaXbxLIse1YQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/ysl-sparkle-clash-holiday-2016-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YSL 圣诞限量彩妆系列曝光</a>。该系列名为 Sparkle Clash，走的是金光闪闪的华丽风格。囊括了唇膏、指甲油、四色眼影等多款彩妆单品。其中，唇膏的膏体上还有特别的星星印记。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101022089Zgpj8cQ0JsGV1EL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102215oMRjZw6m9xl3zuc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102233kWNBsz0XPOml7bjg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102233ie5hra80cVYqMw6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102233pQf5e2DjlaLUiOCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102233Qy1dJOaX2hVU0Ief.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102234K9tn46iseFHJGPMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102234IJK6rpfB4qziOAZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010102241ZSQHlqEU1DLcFovG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">街头艺术大师 KAWS 与 Pace Prints 合作推出丝网印刷版画，这幅作品以 Snoopy 为主角，融入了 KAWS 招牌式的撞色涂鸦元素，全球限量发售 50 幅。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100435EhceBC4OtKDgvZpr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/j-crew-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">J.Crew 完整公开了 2017 春夏 lookbook</a>，延续了以往的休闲混搭正装的风格，并加入了缤纷的色彩。该系列共计 28 个造型，我们挑选了其中的几套，都还挺好看的。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100447Eqr4GNAT3adlWf2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101004477yfL50ecNF1ujgqn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100447JWXk9KGoturvnylZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100447kSA9guxaw0jBT8Wb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100447JgKwbXZPO2ldeVon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100447LHXZP9ilpB3cMfUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100448UF93N7ozi1SmjOqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100448icBdqOotRJ1Qfvpe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100450pudVQnUbF0PZgY2X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010100459LU1FhR5aWJCuKg78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为了纪念进入日本 30 周年，意大利牛仔品牌 Diesel 与时装设计师裕子小池百合子（Yuko Koike）合作推出了一个向日本文化致敬的系列。系列中将日本和服风和牛仔蓝色布料相结合。除此之外，<a href=\"http://www.designboom.cn/news/201610/%E4%BC%8A%E5%8A%BF%E4%B8%B9%E7%99%BE%E8%B4%A7Diesel%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E6%A9%B1%E7%AA%97_10139.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">30 周年活动</a>还包括出售限量牛仔蓝的限量衍生品和时装秀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010101443VymPWtXxkJdDiU7n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010101452U7AzxZ4NT2JrCVLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010101452BQATvOEoKzPLyMfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101014525roGSMNc2f6IxJ1A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010101905GaBNzFpMQPtRA0Eo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010101910ql5iXS9bvAWjPaL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760976\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}